com.gembox.spreadsheet.internal.sortfilter

Class ColorFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gembox.spreadsheet.Filter
      • com.gembox.spreadsheet.internal.sortfilter.ColorFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CellFormatDataFormatHolder

    public final class ColorFilter
extends Filter
implements CellFormatDataFormatHolder
    Represents a filter that specifies the style (with fill or font color) to filter by and whether to use the cell's fill or font color in the filter criteria.

      • isFont

        public boolean isFont()

        Gets a value indicating whether or not to filter by the cell's font color. true indicates to filter by cell's font color. false indicates to filter by the cell's fill color.

        Default value is false.

        Returns:
        true if font; otherwise, false.

      • setFont

        public void setFont(boolean value)

        Gets a value indicating whether or not to filter by the cell's font color. true indicates to filter by cell's font color. false indicates to filter by the cell's fill color.

        Default value is false.

        Parameters:
        value - true if font; otherwise, false.
